      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-sgl-vlt        not  = c-sgl
                     go to pmt-bas-lst-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione prompt                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      14                   to   v-car                  .
           move      11                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      54                   to   v-pos                  .
